main event: A sighting of an unidentified flying object was reported in Cumberland, Maryland on July 26, 1965.
interesting points: The sighting was officially logged in the Project Blue Book records., No photographs were confirmed to accompany the report., The observer submitted a request for results regarding investigations of the incident., Analysis indicated that positive identification of the object was unlikely due to poor processing of submitted photographs., The report mentioned that some points of interest were plotted on a blue water tower in the area.
witness description: The document refers to an observer but does not provide further details about their identity.
